data.description: FANTASTIC 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom END-UNIT townhome in sought after “Williamsburg Village” with loads of upgrades. The entire main level features wide open floor plan with plenty of natural light and newly installed luxury vinyl wood plank flooring. Updated kitchen showcases white wood cabinets on top and complimentary blue cabinets on the bottom. Decorative wood backsplash, recessed lighting, large island with two stools, butcher block top and wainscoting. The pantry is conveniently tucked away in the corner. Adjacent living room with cozy gas fireplace has a door that leads to the back deck and private rear yard. The perfect place to enjoy a cocktail around the fire pit with friends. HUGE two-story great room is where you will want to put up your 13 foot tree in front of the wall of windows. The 2nd floor balcony overlooks this room. Formal dining room has beautiful bay window and crown moldings. The powder room has pedestal sink, shiplap accent wall and antique bronze fixtures. Upstairs you will find a large master bedroom with walk-in closet, private bath with dual vanity, soaking tub and separate shower. Two other spacious bedrooms, another full bathroom and convenient 2nd floor laundry room complete this level. The 4th bedroom is located on the 3rd floor. All 4 bedrooms have ceiling fans. There is a huge unfinished basement for storage. Other amenities include: 1 car garage, NEW front door and NEWLY installed A/C system with transferrable warranty. This home is located on one of the largest and most desirable lots in the neighborhood. Perfect location. Loads of privacy but also use of extra parking area that is usually empty. Neutral decor throughout will make decorating a breeze. Only minutes to Merck, lots of restaurants and shopping options, PA turnpike and all major roadways.  NORTH PENN SCHOOL DISTRICT! Make your appointment today!
